The paper deals with enhancing and restoring images, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The specific focus on underwater images suggests that graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) could also be relevant sub-categories. The use of image quality metrics and CNN-based approach suggests that artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) could also be relevant sub-categories.
